      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice. the reality is that i'm just another person in a sea of millions. if i wasn't here, the world would just keep spinning like nothing happened. it actually feels more peaceful to think about just... fading out. like, if nothing matters, then there's no point in struggling to stay visible anymore.",
